print("Customer signups have steadily increased over the past few years, indicating a successful customer acquisition strategy. Further expanding marketing during this growth phase could capture additional customers.")
print("\nBusiness Insight 4: Seasonal Transaction Trends")
print("Transaction volumes spike during the fourth quarter, indicating seasonal demand. Leveraging this data for seasonal promotions and stock management could maximize sales during peak times.")
